OL,7,FA woman from Merthyr Tydfil says
OL,8,Fpeople need be "more aware" when is
OL,9,Fcomes to understanding epilepsy.
OL,11,FMelissa Davidge, 42, was diagnosed
OL,12,Fwith the condition as a child, and
OL,13,Ftakes around 14 tablets a day to help
OL,14,Fwith the severity and frequency of her
OL,15,Fseizures.
