OL,7,FOver the years, her seizures have led
OL,8,Fto numerous accidents, including
OL,9,Fbroken bones. In one serious incident,
OL,10,Fshe fell into a hot bath during an
OL,11,Fepisode, resulting in third-degree
OL,12,Fburns and a month-long hospital stay.
OL,14,FDaily tasks present a challenge for
OL,15,FMelissa, who depends on her family for
OL,16,Fsupport, with her sister helping with
OL,17,Ftasks like ironing to prevent serious
OL,18,Faccidents.
