OL,7,F"People should understand that there
OL,8,Fare more than one type of seizures...
OL,9,Fthey always think you're going to fall
OL,10,Fto the floor, start shaking and that's
OL,11,Fthe tonic-clonic seizure, but there
OL,12,Fare many types of different seizures
OL,13,Fyou can have," she said.
OL,15,F"Sometimes I can just be drifting into
OL,16,Fspace, or in my own little world. My
OL,17,Ffamily can understand and recognise
OL,18,Fit... but there are loads of different
OL,19,Ftypes and people should understand
OL,20,Fthat."
