OL,7,FHer husband Kevin Davidge helps to
OL,8,Fcare for Melissa. He said despite days
OL,9,Fwhen there are no seizures, they never
OL,10,Fknow when the next is coming.
OL,12,F"You have to be on high alert all the
OL,13,Ftime," he said.
OL,15,FA new report by Epilepsy Action Cymru
OL,16,Ffound every single health board in
OL,17,FWales is failing to meet treatment
OL,18,Fstandards for a first epileptic
OL,19,Fseizure.
