OL,4,Cepilepsy as report shows health board
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FNational Institute for Health and Care
OL,8,FExcellence (NICE) guidelines state
OL,9,Fpatients should be seen by specialists
OL,10,Fwithin two weeks of having their first
OL,11,Fseizure, but no health board in Wales
OL,12,Fis meeting this target, with 43% of
OL,13,Fpatients not being referred to a
OL,14,Fspecialist service after their first
OL,15,Fseizure.
OL,17,FThe report also highlights Wales is
OL,18,Ffacing a neurology workforce shortage.
OL,19,FWhile some progress has been made, the
OL,20,Fcharity says this not enough to give
OL,21,Fpatients the care they need.
