OL,7,FJanet Paterson, Wales manager at
OL,8,FEpilepsy Action, said: "There is still
OL,9,Fso much to be done to reach the right
OL,10,Flevel of care for people with epilepsy
OL,11,Fin Wales. We're nowhere near where we
OL,12,Fneed to be.
OL,14,F"Too many patients keep telling us
OL,15,Fthey're waiting months for an
OL,16,Fappointment, or they can't get a hold
OL,17,Fof a neurologist because they have too
OL,18,Fmany patients. And the data speaks.
OL,19,FIt's practically impossible to serve a
OL,20,Fpopulation of over 30,000 people with
OL,21,Fepilepsy with a dozen specialists.
